  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add toasted fregola and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add kombu cold extract and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 15 minutes or until fregola is tender.",
    "Stir in heavy cream and cook for 2 minutes or until creamy.",
    "Add grana padano cheese and cook until melted and smooth.",
    "Add cooked chicken breast and cook until heated through.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
  ],
